title: Marvel Spiderman
description: Hold onto your chimichangas, folks. From the studio that brought you all 3 Taken films comes the block-busting, fourth-wall-breaking masterpiece about Marvel Comics sexiest anti-hero! Starring Gods perfect idiot Ryan Reynolds and a bunch of other actors, DEADPOOL is a giddy slice of awesomeness packed with more twists than Deadpools enemies intestines and more action than prom night. Amazeballs!
